title: Inner London ( UK ) : population 2011 , by ethnic group
summary: This is a bar chart. It shows Share of population for 6 number of Ethnic Groupss.
The Share of population is appeared to be the highest at Ethnic Groups White and lowest at Ethnic Groups Gypsy/Traveller/Irish traveller.
There is a difference of 57.2 between the maximum Ethnic Groups White and minimum Ethnic Groups Gypsy/Traveller/Irish traveller.

max_summary: This bar chart has 6 columns on the x axis representing Ethnic Groups, and Share of population in each Ethnic Groups on the y axis.
The Share of population is appeared to be the highest at Ethnic Groups White and lowest at Ethnic Groups Gypsy/Traveller/Irish traveller.
Ethnic Groups Black / African / Caribbean / Black British has the second highest value for Share of population.
There is a difference of 57.2 between the maximum Ethnic Groups White and minimum Ethnic Groups Gypsy/Traveller/Irish traveller.

Ethnic Groups White is higher than any other Ethnic Groupss with value 57.3, followed by Black / African / Caribbean / Black British, and Asian / Asian British. Down to Ethnic Groups Gypsy/Traveller/Irish traveller with the lowest value 0.1.
Considered together, the average Share of population in all 6 Ethnic Groupss is roughly 16.72.
Summing up the values of all Ethnic Groupss, we get total 100.3.
